<title>USA: FTP Software may not reach '97 revenue aims.</title>
<headline>FTP Software may not reach '97 revenue aims.</headline>
<dateline>ANDOVER, Mass. 1997-04-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>FTP Software Inc said Thursday that because financial results for the first quarter, Ended March 31, fell below the company's internal revenue goals, it believes that it will be difficult to achieve its internal goal of 25 percent to 30 percent in revenue growth for 1997.</p>
<p>FTP reported a net loss of $11 million, or $0.33 per share, in the first quarter, while revenues from continuing operations fell to $21.4 million from $26.8 million, year to year.</p>
